# Import libraries

```{r}
library(tidyverse)
```

# Read the data

```{r}
data <- read.delim("Data/lib_debloat_status_per_version.csv", sep = ",", header = T, stringsAsFactors = TRUE)
```

# Plot debloated versions per library

```{r}
data %>% filter(NbDebloatedVersions == 0)


data %>% summarise(sum(NbVersions))



```
